commit.message: Added inventory with add/remove ingredient options. Added authentecation.
removed duplicate entry in ingredient dataset and recomputed ingredient matrix

Scipts to get matrix of cosine difference (ingredientMatrix) complete

New Class IngredientMatcher now uses method computeIngredientMatrix to create a matrix that maps every ingredient to every ingredient in a cell of their cosine difference.

This matrix will be used to find Ingredients that are similar to each other.
Added front-end; Added view functions and templates
fixed duplicate ingredient id from pepper to 1532

algorithm to fit matchingMatrix complete

finished algorithm to match every ingredient with every compound's idf in a matrix where each column except for the first is a different compound.

Also exports and saves the data from the matrix in csv file matching_matrix.csv

IDF algorithm implemented

IDF Algorithm now correctly adds an extra column to ingredients_compounds matrix labelled uniqueness that contains the tf idf of that compound for that ingredient
